Subject: drm/amd/display: fix memory leak when using debugfs_lookup()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: cbfac7fa491651c57926c99edeb7495c6c1aeac2
